NormFiberVelocity
version=1
nRows=101
nColumns=87
inDegrees=no

This analysis gathers basic information about muscles during a simulation (e.g., forces, tendon lengths, moment arms, etc).
Units are S.I. units (second, meters, Newtons, ...)
If the header above contains a line with 'inDegrees', this indicates whether rotational values are in degrees (yes) or radians (no).

